{"tid":2063378,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Microsoft及Amazon暫停向警察提供人臉識別技術服務，IBM永久退出","createTime":"2020-06-14T02:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T03:51:27.000Z","uid":48040,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9b2fa7af42664b9aaf60fe639dea66b8f2b0f5","tid":2063378,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"繼Amazon與IBM 等公司決定停止暫停向美國政府部門或私人企業，提供與支援現有的人臉辨識應用後，Microsoft總裁Brad Smith 也加入表態，指出在規範該技術的全國性法律公佈之前，該公司絕不會向美國警方出售人臉辨識應用。<br />\n<br />\n根據亞馬遜之前對外公佈，將暫停支援現時向美國警方供應人臉辨識應用12 個月，更指出國家需要更明確與嚴格的法規，以規範相關道德水平，更認為一年足以讓國會找尋最好的回應方式。另一方面，IBM 的態度更加決絕，已表示會完全退出人臉辨識的業務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2668788/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E4%B8%8D%E5%94%AE%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%89%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2668788%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2594%25AE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%2589%25E8%25AD%2598%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJrO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=fa18ddff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2668788/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E4%B8%8D%E5%94%AE%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%89%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business-53006438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fbusiness-53006438&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJrO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=4030fafc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fbusiness-53006438&h=238b106f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business-53006438</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0